Preheat oven to 350 degrees F. Cut avocados in half, remove pit. Scoop out small portion of each avocado with teaspoon. Fill each avocado half with 1 to 2 tablespoons of BUSH'S(R) Sriracha Beans; top with 2 tablespoons of shredded cheese. Place avocados on baking sheet; bake for 15 minutes or until cheese is melted. Serve immediately. Garnish avocados with Mexican crema or sour cream, if desired.